\h SHOW \d

\uUSAGE\n
show item \s...\d person

\uDESCRIPTION\n
Show one or more items in your inventory and/or readied equipment to another person.

To show the ring in your inventory to Hanako:
\qshow \li#l\qring hanako\d4`
...or just...
\qshow ring hanako\d4`

To show the ring in your readied equipment to Hanako:
\qshow \le#l\qring hanako\d4`

\uEXAMPLES\n
\qshow ring \le#l\qbracelet hanako\d to show the ring in your inventory and the bracelet in your readied equipment to Hanako.4`
\qshow \p2#i\qring hanako\d to show the second ring in your inventory to Hanako.4`
\qshow \le#l\p2#m\qbracelet hanako\d to show the first two bracelets in your readied equipment to Hanako.4`
\qshow \p3#i\qring \le#l\p3#m\qbracelet hanako\d to show the third ring in your inventory and the first three bracelets in your readied equipment to Hanako.4`
\qshow \p#a\qring \le#l\p#a\qbracelet hanako\d to show all of the rings in your inventory and all of the bracelets in your readied equipment to Hanako.4`
\qshow \p#a\q hanako\d to show all of the items in your inventory to Hanako.4`
\qshow \le#l\p#a\q hanako\d to show all of the items in your readied equipment to Hanako.4`
\qshow \p5#m\qgp \p#a\qsp hanako\d to show five of your gold pieces and all of your silver pieces to Hanako.4`
\qshow \p#a\qcoin hanako\d to show all of your coins to Hanako.4`

\uSEE ALSO\n
